---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about" number="02" label="about">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <h2 class="font-mono text-base font-medium text-[var(--color-text)] mb-5">
      Juan Iznardo
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Computer Engineer finishing my degree in Spain. Before committing to a specialization,
        I'm deliberately exploring across the stack — from low-level systems to infrastructure
        — to understand where I want to go deep.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently building a Game Boy emulator in C to learn how CPUs and memory actually work.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm interested in the business side of things too — how products get built,
        how they reach people, and what makes them worth building.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
